        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h1><p>这是一个Minecraft整合包合集页面，包含从1.18.2起由我打包的各类整合包，以生电向mod为主<br/><br>整合包一般都会包含以下mod，无特殊情况不再重复描述：</p><details> <summary> 展开mod列表 </summary><table><thead><tr><th>mod名称</th><th>下载地址</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>AppleSkin</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/appleskin">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/EsAfCjCV">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Architectury</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/architectury-api">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/lhGA9TYQ">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Auth Me</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/auth-me">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/yjgIrBjZ">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>AutoFish</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/autofish">Curseforge</a></td></tr><tr><td>Bad Packets</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/badpackets">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/ftdbN0KK">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Better Beds</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-beds">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/kKwy3HU9">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>CIT Resewn</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cit-resewn">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/otVJckYQ">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Carpet Mod</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/carpet">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/TQTTVgYE">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Carpet Extra</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/carpet-extra">Curseforge</a> &#x2F; <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/VX3TgwQh">Modrinth</a></td></tr><tr><td>Carpet TCTC Addition</td><td><a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/carpet-tctc-addition">Curseforge</a> &#x2F;